ANNOTATION
the final qualifying work
______________________________                                                 

On the topic : Tax risks and ways of their minimization in the Russian Federation.
Final qualifying work consists of 67 pages, 3 chapters, 2 tables, 3 drawing, list of used sources of literature, 4 apps. 
Final qualification work consists of 68 pages without appendices, 3 heads, 17 tables, 9 drawings, the list of the used literature, 4 appendices. 
Keywords: tax burden, tax risk, system of the taxation, the general system of the taxation, the simplified system of the taxation.
Object of research is practice of management of tax risks in LLC Prava i pravo.
The purpose of work is the analysis of functioning of system of the taxation of the organization and development of offers on decrease in tax risks of the organizations. 
Final qualification work consists of introduction, three heads, the conclusion and the list of the used literature.
In introduction relevance of the chosen research subject is formulated, the purpose and problems of work, object and a subject, structure of work is presented.
Chapter 1 opens bases of management of tax risks, methods of management over them. Chapter 2 is devoted to the analysis of practice of the taxation of LLC Prava i pravo and an assessment of degree of tax risks in the organization. 
The chapter 3 contains offers on decrease in tax burden of LLC Prava i pravo and the recommendation about management of tax risks.
In the conclusion conclusions, fundamental on work, are defined.
In work methods of the system analysis, strategic analysis, methods of forecasting, the analysis of documents, supervision were used.
